<!-- tomat mark for the launch splash. One vector, tinted per theme via
     @color/splash_logo (dark in light mode, white in dark mode). The path is
     scaled to ~2/3 of the canvas so it sits inside the circular safe zone the
     Android 12+ splash masks the icon into. -->
